    Tankkor and Tarantulas cruised into the battle scene. Tankkor i nhis tank 
mode, Tarantulas in his cycle mode.
    "I hope were not to late, hehehehe." He then sped out from the red wood, 
full speed, and was on a course to slam into Killfest.
    Tankkor transformed, and opened fire. He picked random targets.

    Gremlin watched the maps. He didnt understand what was going on. He knew 
thier was a secret mission in progress....but why were there holograms on the 
map? It didnt make sense at all. 
    "Hell Beast, what do you make of these holograms?" Gremlin asked, turning 
to the Commander.
    "Interesting, " he said, "I dont know. Have one of the bots 
investigate.Im sure it has something to do with this mission....and begin to 
decode this transmission from War to Killfest."

    Putnam, Odiphious, and Venus see Akron n the midst of battle. The join 
her, armed and ready. "Wheres the rat?" Putnam asked. Akron shot at her 
several time, and the other Energonians too kthier spots and joined it.

    Ominous looked at Quasar. In the Orb, they were alone. She should be 
waking up at any moment...
